						<div class="postbody">First I <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/search.php?keywords=lorom+hirom+name" class="postlink">searched</a> to see if there was already an answer. Not finding one, I asked in the closest topic that fit. I guess my preference for a necro over a dupe is informed by the classic Flash slideshow &quot;Posting and You&quot; (<a href="http://www.albinoblacksheep.com/flash/posting" class="postlink">SWF</a> | <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gx4EfoLzu_I" class="postlink">YouTube</a>).</div>

